node.text:
OFF THE RAILS 7-ELEVEN EXCLUSIVE FLAVOR!skateboard
.
police car lightWe are BRINGING THE BANG with the new Bang Energy Swirly Pop Flavor Launch exclusively at 7-Eleven! On July 11th, make sure to celebrate this epic event by picking up the all #NEW Swirly Pop Bang Energy and getting a #FREE Slurpee! 
.
Bang Energy is celebrating with a #giveaway of some exclusive Swirly Pop collab-themed gear! Check out how you can enter to win an exclusive hat, T-shirt, skateboard, deck stickers, and a free case of the NEW Swirly Pop!
keycap: 1FEED POST a photo of you with your purchased Swirly Pop from 7-Eleven.
keycap: 2TAG @BangEnergy, @BangEnergy.CEO & #SwirlyPop
keycap: 3SIGN-UP at BangEnergyGiveaway.com (entrants who skip this step won't be eligible).
.
5 Winners will be chosen and announced on the Bang Energy IG Story Friday 7/16.
.
Follow the inventor of Bang: @BangEnergy.CEOsmiling face with sunglasses
.
